    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use a real iterator.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Iterator&lt;Object&gt; it = map.keySet().iterator();\n\nwhile (it.hasNext())\n{\n  it.next();\n  if (something)\n    it.remove();\n }\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Actually, you might need to iterate over the <code>entrySet()</code> instead of the <code>keySet()</code> to make that work.</p>\n"
