      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "You should use the entrySet instead of using the keySet and doing a get every time. FindBugs even has a detector for this: <a href=\"http://findbugs.sourceforge.net/bugDescriptions.html#WMI_WRONG_MAP_ITERATOR\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">findbugs.sourceforge.net/&hellip;</a>"
