    "question_id" : 1884889,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As of Java 8 you could do this as follows:</p>\n<pre><code>map.entrySet().removeIf(e -&gt; &lt;boolean expression&gt;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Oracle Docs: <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Map.html#entrySet--\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>entrySet()</code></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The set is backed by the map, so changes to the map are reflected in the set, and vice-versa</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
