    "body" : "<pre><code>Set s=map.entrySet();\nIterator iter = s.iterator();\n\nwhile (iter.hasNext()) {\n    Map.Entry entry =(Map.Entry)iter.next();\n\n    if(\"value you need to remove\".equals(entry.getKey())) {\n         map.remove();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
