  "question_id" : 1884889,
  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1884889/iterating-over-and-removing-from-a-map",
  "closed_reason" : "Duplicate",
  "title" : "iterating over and removing from a map",
  "body" : "<p>I was doing:</p>\n<pre><code>for (Object key : map.keySet())\n    if (something)\n        map.remove(key);\n</code></pre>\n<p>which threw a ConcurrentModificationException, so i changed it to:</p>\n<pre><code>for (Object key : new ArrayList&lt;Object&gt;(map.keySet()))\n    if (something)\n        map.remove(key);\n</code></pre>\n<p>this, and any other procedures that modify the map are in synchronized blocks.</p>\n<p><strong>is there a better solution?</strong></p>\n"
}